        "Some people think bicycle has more advantages while others bicycle had a lot of advantages.As far as my opinion is concerned, I will go with the advantages of the bicycle because of the following reasons.",
        "To begin with,the advantages of the bicycle are if you are riding a bicycle you will remain fit because riding a bicycle is one of the best exercises.In the  gym there are also stationary bicycles to do exercise the best advantage is that your belly will remain fit and you will be not fat. Furthermore, another advantage is that if you are going to school or a job you don't have to pay because you are going by  bicycle.Nowadays people use bicycles to go to job or anywhere because they want to be fit.",
